{"tid":669613,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿迪達好有可能接掌阿仙奴!!","createTime":"2018-05-18T15:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T17:28:16.000Z","uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"56e387ca575a1d4bbd9bb73d95dd281469bf56e7","tid":669613,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"阿迪達成阿仙奴新帥大熱<br />\n<br />\n傳奇主帥雲格離任，對於阿仙奴下任領隊外間都有不同說法。根據最新消息，在艾歷尼聲言留效祖雲達斯後，阿仙奴的管理層屬意讓前球員阿迪達回巢領導球隊。<br />\n<br />\n自雲格宣布季後離隊的消息後，「老婦人」主帥艾歷尼一直都是接手的大熱人選，惟這個意大利名帥日前自己會留效都靈，令阿仙奴管理層不得不向「Plan B」阿迪達埋手。現年36歲的阿迪達球員時代曾是「槍手」一員，目前為曼城助教，據指他已獲多名高層力撐接手阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n當前球壇少帥風氣甚盛，像哥迪奧拿、施蒙尼及普捷天奴等都未滿50歲，惟阿迪達如真以36歲之齡接掌英超勁旅如阿仙奴，相信絕對會成為一時佳話。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=8HhhJffOGWxBLVTaJGqiT54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c01e0046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>rteta<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>rsene<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>rsenal</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72418400b430bd31d646dbda0f04b35e91c2e9c","tid":669613,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>A</strong>lex iwobi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76279f25f2d501895a19383bac06f08c9d3a90f","tid":669613,"uid":22589,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f72418400b430bd31d646dbda0f04b35e91c2e9c","tid":669613,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>A</strong>lex iwobi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"呢個係垃圾 唔洗理會"},{"pid":"2fc468df478a382c1ed16d682576d46a2ccc8198","tid":669613,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi